claim.claim-text:
An automatic-metering wireless device attached to a meter device having a magnetic generator, the wireless device comprising:
a body;
a readout reed switch for sensing magnetism generated by the magnetic generator;
a projection protruding from the body in a first direction, and disposed in a recess of the meter device and including the readout reed switch;
a first securing part for securing the body in the first direction with respect to the meter device; and
a second securing part for securing the body in a second direction substantially orthogonal to the first direction, with respect to the meter device.
